  "texts": [
    "Meanwhile, the channel-attention mechanism selectively emphasizes important feature channels while suppressing irrelevant background information, resulting in more refined feature representation and improved classification performance.",
    "This proposed mechanism helps our network excel in handling the inter-class similarity and high intra-class variability.Our experimental results, based on three benchmark datasets (RSSCN7, PatternNet, and EuroSAT), demonstrate the RCA network's superior performance, with classification accuracies of 97%, 99%, and 96%, respectively.",
    "These results show that the RCA network not only outperforms existing state-of-the-art methods but also significantly reduces computational complexity, particularly in challenging scenarios with limited training data and complex image backgrounds.",
    "Visualization using Grad-CAM further validated the effectiveness of our approach, confirming the network's ability to focus on the most critical image features.",
    "In light of these findings, we recommend extending the application of the RCA network to other remote sensing tasks, such as object detection and change detection."
  ],
